New stuff, refer to the ChangeLog for a more detailed description of
the changes.

0.5.8
-----
- Screenshot plugin moved from PNG into JPEG
- XVideo support added (XvPutImage and XvPutVideo)
- Russian freq table (Eugene Crosser), Cyrillic Teletext glyphs
	(Sergey Nikulin)
- V4L2 support into libvbi.
- Updated fr.po (Christian), es.po (me) added ru.po (Sergey) and
	de.po (Michael).
- Many bugfixes, some new bugs to play with :-)
